FIRST STEP BLAST: NEED TO HAVE BLAST LOADED


1. runtblastn.pl -- run tblastn of reference peptides against blast database
2. getsequencetoretrieve.pl -- makes gene files with top hits from blast
3. runretrieveseq.pl -- uses blastdbcmd to pull sequences from blast db

