BLAST SHORT READS AGAINST THE REFERENCE DNA

6. 6-runblast.pl
7. 7-getexons.pl  -- will read through the blast output and pull only the sequence that matched (exons) reverse transcribe if necessary.

ALIGN SHORT READS TO REFERENCE GENE USING MUSCLE

8. 8-makealignmentfiles.pl -- need reference DNA reads
9. 9-runmuscle.pl -- need muscle program -- strong gap opening penalty

CREATE CONSENSUS FILES PER GENE

10. makefastafrommuscle.pl
11. makeconsensussequence.pl



